# XBF testdata

synthetic_minimal.xbf: hand-built minimal XBF v2.1 fixture, generated by
TestMain in decoder_test.go (regenerates the file on every test run if
missing or stale). Byte-level layout mirrors the structure described in
misenhower/XbfAnalyzer (C#, archived) — it is a synthetic re-creation, not
a Microsoft asset.

The fixture encodes the equivalent of:

  <Page xmlns="http://schemas.microsoft.com/winfx/2006/xaml/presentation"
        xmlns:x="http://schemas.microsoft.com/winfx/2006/xaml"
        x:Class="App.MainPage">
    <Grid>
      <Button Content="Click Me"/>
    </Grid>
  </Page>

Regenerate by running:
  go test ./pkg/winui/xaml/xbf -run TestRegenerateSyntheticMinimal -v

synthetic_minimal.xaml: golden output for the decoder; whitespace-tolerant
comparison applied in TestDecodeXBF_SyntheticMinimal.

Origin: synthesized in-repo (no Microsoft IP).
